{"id":82,"date":"2025-08-25T11:56:43","date_gmt":"2025-08-25T06:26:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=82"},"modified":"2025-08-31T02:56:51","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:26:51","slug":"our-events","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/our-events\/","title":{"rendered":"Our Events"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/events-scaled-e1756491795902.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/events-scaled-e1756491795902.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">Celebrating Service, Inspiring Change \u2013Our Events <\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cEvery event of the Lions Club of Balasore is more than a gathering\u2014it is a movement of compassion, unity, and purpose. Through our service programs, awareness campaigns, fundraisers, and community celebrations, we bring people together to create impact that lasts beyond the moment. Each event is an opportunity to serve, to learn, to lead, and to inspire others to join the journey of humanity. Whether it is a local outreach or a global initiative, our events shine as milestones of dedication, friendship, and hope. They remind us that when hearts unite in service, ordinary days turn into extraordinary memories, and together, we build a stronger, brighter tomorrow.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\r\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/join-now\/\" class=\"ispl-hero-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.9rem 1.5rem; background:#ffcc00; color:#111; text-decoration:none; border-radius:.35rem; font-weight:600;\">\r\n                            Get Involved                        <\/a>\r\n                    <\/p>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/section>\r\n        \n\t\t<style>\r\n\t\t\/* Filter tabs *\/\r\n\t\t.events-filters { \/*display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;*\/ text-align:center; margin:0 0 16px; }\r\n\t\t.events-filters a {\r\n\t\t\tdisplay:inline-block; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:9px;\r\n\t\t\tborder:1px solid #e0e0e0; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; font-size:14px;margin:5px;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t.events-filters a.is-active { background:#1976d2; color:#fff; border-color:#1976d2; }\r\n\t\t.events-filters a:hover { border-color:#9e9e9e; }\r\n\r\n\t\t\/* Ribbon bookmark top-right *\/\r\n\t\t.event-card { position: relative; }\r\n\t\t.event-ribbon {\r\n\t\t\tposition:absolute; top:10px; right:-8px;\r\n\t\t\tpadding:6px 12px; color:#fff; font-weight:700; font-size:12px;\r\n\t\t\tborder-top-left-radius:6px; border-bottom-left-radius:6px;\r\n\t\t\tbox-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.15); z-index:2;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t.event-ribbon.upcoming { background:#fb8c00; } \/* orange *\/\r\n\t\t.event-ribbon.ongoing  { background:#2e7d32; } \/* green *\/\r\n\t\t.event-ribbon.past     { background:#d32f2f; } \/* red *\/\r\n\r\n\t\t.blog-entry .block-20 { display:block; background-size:cover; background-position:center; width:100%; aspect-ratio:2\/3; }\r\n\t\t.events-pagination { display:flex; justify-content:center; margin:24px 0; }\r\n\t\t.events-pagination .page-numbers {\r\n\t\t\tdisplay:inline-block; margin:0 4px; padding:8px 12px; border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none;\r\n\t\t}\